title: Beta Web App
description: The Beta Web App is currently available to try free-of-charge, click here to sign up.. You can check the uptime status by clicking here. This purpose of this is to simply test the agentic experience where SELF learns about each user during conversations (likes, dislikes, traits, habits, places you've been, goals, dreams etc.), and generates a user profile. You may also create your profile through manual input.
